abstracts.cdata!:
The project would comprise: (a) about 80
            man-years of consulting services to: (i) prepare
            pre-investment studies and feasibility studies for high
            priority productive investments mainly, but not exclusively,
            in the industrial, mining, transport and communications
            sectors; and (ii) conduct special studies at the sector and
            firm level; (b) Overseas training for Tanzanians in project
            preparation, evaluation, implementation and related
            techniques; and (c) a project unit and related supporting services.
